Package: scTenifoldNet.lite
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight and Accelerated Gene Regulatory Network Comparison for 
    Single-Cell Transcriptomics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(
    given = "Yuchen", family = "Li", 
    email = "ycli1995@outlook.com", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Fast and memory-efficient implementation of the scTenifoldNet 
    workflow for constructing and comparing single-cell gene regulatory 
    networks. The computational performance for principal component regression, 
    tensor decomposition, and manifold alignment was optimized, while preserving 
    the core analytical framework of the original scTenifoldNet method. 
